                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A homunculus has one dose of poison in a reservoir in its head. It can refill this poison from its reserves with an Interact action</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[fortitude|dc:15]</p><hr /><p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Damage[1d6[poison]] and @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} (1 round).</p>"
